### EduPortal API - Study Abroad Controller
### Study abroad program management endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:5000
### Requires Authentication

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/study-abroad
@contentType = application/json
@token = {{$dotenv TOKEN}}

### ===========================================
### GET ALL PROGRAMS - (Admin, Coach, Danışman)
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET ACTIVE PROGRAMS - (Admin, Coach, Danışman)
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/active
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET PROGRAM SUMMARIES - (Admin, Coach, Danışman)
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/summaries
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET PROGRAM BY ID
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET PROGRAMS BY STUDENT
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/student/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET PROGRAMS BY COACH - (Admin, Coach, Danışman)
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/coach/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET STATISTICS - (Admin, Coach, Danışman)
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### CREATE PROGRAM - (Admin, Coach, Danışman)
### ===========================================
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "studentId": 1,
  "coachId": 1,
  "programName": "USA Summer Program",
  "university": "Harvard University",
  "country": "USA",
  "city": "Cambridge",
  "startDate": "2025-06-01",
  "endDate": "2025-08-31",
  "status": "Applied",
  "notes": "Yaz okulu başvurusu"
}

### ===========================================
### UPDATE PROGRAM - (Admin, Coach, Danışman)
### ===========================================
PUT {{baseUrl}}/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "status": "Accepted",
  "notes": "Başvuru kabul edildi, vize sürecine geçilecek"
}

### ===========================================
### DELETE PROGRAM - (Admin only)
### ===========================================
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
